  "merger_description": "The Acquirer, Genea Pty Ltd (**Genea**) operates an IVF and fertility business with clinics in NSW, the ACT, Victoria, Queensland, Western Australia and South Australia. Genea operates a clinic in Bowen Hills, Queensland, and an entity related to Genea (**Adora Holdco Pty Ltd**) operates a bulk-billed IVF clinic, Adora Fertility, in Taringa, Queensland.\n\nGenea proposes to acquire a single independent clinic, Care Fertility Greenslopes Pty Ltd (**Care Fertility**), along with an associated trust (Care Fertility Greenslopes Unit Trust) and intellectual property\u00a0(the\u00a0**Acquisition**). Care Fertility is\u00a0a gynaecology, IVF and fertility business located in Greenslopes, Queensland that is ultimately owned and controlled by Dr Clare Boothroyd.",
